query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `cycle_analytics_cache` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `cycleId` int NOT NULL,
  `analyticsType` enum('backlog','risk','trend','unfunded_critical') NOT NULL,
  `data` text NOT NULL,
  `calculatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `expiresAt` timestamp NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_cycle_analytics` (`cycleId`, `analyticsType`),
  KEY `idx_analytics_expiry` (`expiresAt`)
)
